      "content": "hey so im 20 weeks pregnant and i have this insane sinus infection. my head is pounding and i can't breathe through my nose at all. i have some Sudafed in the cabinet from before i was pregnant, is it okay to take a couple of those to help with the pressure so i can actually sleep??",
